data.text:
You can now watch recordings of the sessions from the Sky Italy Summit 2023, sponsored by Tata Communications. Videos are available in Italian, and in Italian with English translation.

Beyond the Screen: Revealing Serie B remote production (Italian version)

Beyond the Screen: Revealing Serie B remote production (English version)

Powering Up The Remote Production: MotoGP case study (Italian version)

Powering Up The Remote Production: MotoGP case study (English version)

Driving Success: Women leading the way in technology (Italian version)

Driving Success: Women leading the way in technology (English version)

The Intersection of Technology and Storytelling (Italian version)

The Intersection of Technology and Storytelling (English version)

Exploring the Future of Sport Technologies and Generative AI (Italian version)

Exploring the Future of Sport Technologies and Generative AI (English version)

Interviews

Ivan Pintabona, CTO of NVP

Paola Montanari, founder of Videe

Scilla Signa CEO, Bridge the Gaps & Founder, Hackher_

The Sky Sport Italy Summit 2023, in conjunction with SVG Europe, took place on 24 May in Milan
